&lt;/p&gt;";s:8:"pub_time";i:1609739661;s:6:"author";s:9:"sunzhihui";s:8:"categ_id";i:2;s:4:"logo";N;s:3:"hot";N;s:6:"status";i:1;}i:5;a:10:{s:2:"id";i:699;s:3:"uid";i:79;s:5:"title";s:74:"沃尔玛低价平板正式发售，搭载安卓系统，最低仅售64刀";s:7:"content";s:3661:"&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 28px; line-height: 32px; text-align: justify; overflow-wrap: break-word; word-break: normal; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: &quot; microsoft=&quot;&quot; yahei&quot;;=&quot;&quot; white-space:=&quot;&quot; normal;=&quot;&quot; background-color:=&quot;&quot; rgb(255,=&quot;&quot; 255,=&quot;&quot; 255);&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;今年年初，有外媒报道，沃尔玛正在尝试推出自己的安卓平板，以对抗亚马逊的平板电脑Fire。本周沃尔玛的Walmart Onn系列平板正式开始发售，最低售价为64美元。
